out a way to pay my share.

05:54.875 --> 05:56.917
REGGIE "REG" WINHORN:
I'm not worried about that.

05:58.833 --> 06:01.500
TUCKER: Start walking. If you
don't remember by the time

06:01.583 --> 06:04.875
you reach that tree, you can
just forget everything, huh?

06:04.958 --> 06:06.500
REG: Hey, look here.

06:06.583 --> 06:08.833
So, the studio movie
starts shooting tomorrow.

06:08.917 --> 06:11.249
U.P.M. called me about
a set costumer thing.

06:11.333 --> 06:12.333
MELISSA: Mm-hm.

06:12.416 --> 06:14.249
Fish-out-of-water story with...

06:14.333 --> 06:16.958
some Australian man who moves
to the Big Apple

06:17.041 --> 06:18.249
and schools us all.

06:20.291 --> 06:22.124
So I put you up for the job.

06:23.041 --> 06:24.667
'Cause I knew you can handle it.

06:26.041 --> 06:27.708
Thank you.

06:27.792 --> 06:30.083
Yeah, well, I gotta look out
for my little partner.

06:30.166 --> 06:31.625
(BOTH CHUCKLE)

06:31.708 --> 06:33.166
I'm the one that's supposed to
be taking care of you.

06:33.249 --> 06:35.999
Well, you are. We're family.

06:40.041 --> 06:43.249
