07:08.208 --> 07:10.999
(DOG BARKING IN DISTANCE)

07:18.249 --> 07:19.541
(SIGHS) I'm out of money.

07:19.625 --> 07:22.041
HARVEY WASSERMAN: Right.
What do you still owe?

07:23.458 --> 07:24.999
Scene to scene?

07:26.166 --> 07:28.625
I mean, half the fucking movie.

07:28.708 --> 07:31.249
Harvey, almost all
of my exteriors.

07:31.333 --> 07:33.708
I don't know what to tell you.

07:33.792 --> 07:35.583
You were gonna peel off
20 for me from

07:35.667 --> 07:37.667
-your straight-to-video stuff.
-I did!

07:37.750 --> 07:40.291
-What are you talking about?
-Well, so-- so what?
-Hey, even though you only

07:40.375 --> 07:42.875
matched it with ten, I still
gave you the 20. What the fuck
you think you've been shooting

07:42.958 --> 07:44.124
-on the last six weeks?
-That's all gone?

07:44.208 --> 07:45.500
All of it. Yes.

07:47.500 --> 07:48.833
All of it.

07:48.917 --> 07:51.541
(SIGHS) Fuck!

07:53.792 --> 07:55.458
I don't wanna lose these actors.

07:55.541 --> 07:58.291
I don't blame you. You know.
I've...

07:58.375 --> 08:00.458
