08:00.541 --> 08:03.792
Look, if I could steal more
for myself to get you there,

08:03.875 --> 08:05.750
I would, but I can't.

08:05.833 --> 08:08.208
We're broke. Maybe I could look
in my wallet

08:08.291 --> 08:09.958
and find you enough to finish

08:10.041 --> 08:11.625
what you have on the schedule
this week,

08:11.708 --> 08:13.166
but that's it.
Afterwards, you know,

08:13.249 --> 08:15.208
you're gonna have to
suspend production.

08:15.291 --> 08:16.875
You know, at least
for the time being.

08:17.750 --> 08:19.041
(CANDY SIGHS)

08:23.750 --> 08:26.124
(INHALES, EXHALES)

08:27.166 --> 08:29.083
What would you do
if you were me?

08:32.041 --> 08:33.708
I'd cast a legend.

08:33.792 --> 08:34.999
Oh, okay.

08:35.083 --> 08:36.166
Well... (SCOFFS)

08:36.249 --> 08:37.708
You're not gonna get any
fresh backing

08:37.792 --> 08:39.208
without any names on this.

08:39.291 --> 08:41.500
You know, there's not a single
porn star in the bunch.

08:41.583 --> 08:43.500
-Okay? There's not one single...
-No, Harvey. They're actors.

08:43.583 --> 08:45.750
-...name for the one-sheet.
-I need them to act.
Fuck porn stars.

08:45.833 --> 08:47.291
Excuse me. You want money,
right?

08:47.375 --> 08:49.500
So, go through your Rolodex,
find someone with fans

08:49.583 --> 08:51.667
who wants a chance to act
in something real,

08:51.750 --> 08:53.416
and then use them in a way
that doesn't ruin

08:53.500 --> 08:55.041
any of the scenes
you really need,

08:55.124 --> 08:58.333
and then make them take
their clothes off and fuck.

08:58.416 --> 08:59.541
Once.

08:59.625 --> 09:00.750
Twice.

09:02.416 --> 09:04.958
A big enough name's gonna
get you that fresh backing.

09:05.041 --> 09:08.041
So, compromise, Eileen.
You know?

09:08.124 --> 09:09.458
It can't all be art.

09:21.041 --> 09:24.583
(COUGHING)

09:25.958 --> 09:27.708
Brought supplies.

09:27.792 --> 09:30.375
-No milk?
-(EXHALES)

09:30.458 --> 09:31.875
Who mixes milk with mash?

09:31.958 --> 09:33.667
Ah. So just the essentials.

09:33.750 --> 09:34.917
(VINCENT CHUCKLES)

09:38.500 --> 09:39.500
So...

09:41.541 --> 09:43.124
What do you think
of this place?

09:44.458 --> 09:46.333
It's pretty much
what I pictured.

09:48.583 --> 09:49.917
Thank you, Vince.

09:49.999 --> 09:52.041
Yeah. Thank the owner.

09:53.500 --> 09:54.917
What's the man's name?

09:54.999 --> 09:57.333
Jerome.

09:57.416 --> 10:01.999
He used to... drink his lunch
in the Hi-Hat, noon to one?

10:02.083 --> 10:03.875
Yeah. I remember.

10:04.667 --> 10:05.833
Good dude.

10:06.958 --> 10:09.041
He said to enjoy it
in good health.

10:09.124 --> 10:12.124
(COUGHS)

10:14.958 --> 10:16.625
Well, that's out of my hands.

10:19.291 --> 10:21.208
Is there anything
I can do for you?

10:24.667 --> 10:26.541
You could finish
splitting that wood.

10:29.833 --> 10:31.041
(CHUCKLES)

10:32.208 --> 10:34.083
All right. (CLEARS THROAT)

10:34.541 --> 10:35.875
(LAUGHS)

10:36.958 --> 10:38.291
Man, you know
what you're doin'?

10:38.375 --> 10:40.833
Please.
It's like riding a bike.

10:42.041 --> 10:43.999
-Just sit back and relax.
-All right.

10:45.541 --> 10:47.625
-I'm out of the business.
-♪ (PIANO MUSIC PLAYS) ♪

10:47.708 --> 10:49.583
I appreciate you reachin' out.

10:49.667 --> 10:51.458
-But I can't.
-EILEEN "CANDY" MERRELL: Okay,

10:51.541 --> 10:53.333
but there's barely
any fucking to be done.

10:53.416 --> 10:54.625
I mean it's-- it's really just

10:54.708 --> 10:55.917
so I can put your name
on the poster

10:55.999 --> 10:57.625
and get some fresh money
behind me.

10:57.708 --> 10:59.083
And what we're doing...

11:01.291 --> 11:02.625
is different...

11:02.708 --> 11:04.500
-Mm-hm.
-...than anything
you or I have ever done.

11:04.583 --> 11:05.958
And you could do some acting.

11:06.041 --> 11:08.333
"Acting." (CHUCKLES)

11:08.416 --> 11:10.124
Who are you bullshitting?

11:10.208 --> 11:11.958
No one ever paid me to act.

11:12.041 --> 11:13.083
(CANDY CHUCKLES)

11:13.166 --> 11:14.625
