11:16.541 --> 11:19.124
Shit, Shana.

11:19.208 --> 11:21.249
If you knew you weren't gonna
take this part,

11:21.333 --> 11:22.750
why'd you agree to meet me?

11:24.124 --> 11:25.375
I'm bored.

11:27.166 --> 11:29.333
I wanted to go to a restaurant
with an old friend,

11:29.416 --> 11:31.416
and... catch up.

11:31.875 --> 11:32.917
Uh-huh.

11:33.833 --> 11:35.833
-Oh, honey.
-(CANDY LAUGHS)

11:35.917 --> 11:37.083
I got married.

11:38.750 --> 11:40.917
-Damn.
-Yeah. (LAUGHS)

11:40.999 --> 11:43.291
To one of the richest
real estate developers

11:43.375 --> 11:45.999
in New York.

11:46.083 --> 11:48.708
Aaron Rivers used to show up
at my movie premieres

11:48.792 --> 11:50.124
in the city and just...

11:50.208 --> 11:52.917
stand in the lobby
and stare at me.

11:52.999 --> 11:55.083
Two dates later he proposed.

11:55.166 --> 11:58.708
He moved me into a 12-bedroom
Tudor revival mansion

11:58.792 --> 11:59.833
in Tuxedo Park

11:59.917 --> 12:02.249
and gave me
an unlimited allowance.

12:03.124 --> 12:04.291
So?

12:04.375 --> 12:07.667
The caveat was
I had to quit the business.

12:09.249 --> 12:10.958
You know where I came from.

12:12.249 --> 12:13.625
I was a star.

12:14.625 --> 12:16.291
And what I had, I earned.

12:17.625 --> 12:19.833
(SIGHS) God.

12:20.958 --> 12:22.792
I loved the attention.

12:22.875 --> 12:25.041
-Yeah.
-I can admit that.

12:25.124 --> 12:27.875
The goddamn attention
was what I loved about it.

12:27.958 --> 12:29.333
Even more than the money.

12:33.833 --> 12:36.999
Now I'm just another woman
living in a gilded cage.

12:41.750 --> 12:42.958
I made a mistake.

12:44.500 --> 12:45.667
What can I say?

12:49.833 --> 12:52.166
Let us have another. Hm?

12:53.083 --> 12:54.166
(CHUCKLES)

12:57.375 --> 13:00.541
